BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20250329T220000Z
DTEND:20250329T230000Z
DTSTAMP:20260320T014627Z
UID:Sinkhole5thAnniversary2025@calendar
URL:https://www.facebook.com/TheSinkholeCraftBeerBar
CREATED:20250222T170537Z
DESCRIPTION:<span>Come help The Sinkhole Craft Beer Bar celebrate 5 years o
 n Saturday March 29th! Bloomington’s own\, overly-educated\, cover band “Do
 n’t Call Me Betty” (DCMB) brings the party to life with a rollicking live r
 ock show of tunes spanning the last 40 years.</span><br><br><br><p></p><p><
 strong>About The Sinkhole Craft Beer Bar:</strong> Located on the south sid
 e of Bloomington\, The Sinkhole offers a warm and inviting atmosphere\, fea
 turing a curated selection of unique beers from local and national brewerie
 s. With a spacious outdoor patio and a commitment to live entertainment\, i
 t’s a favorite spot for both locals and visitors. For more information\, vi
 sit their <a href="https://thesinkhole.beer/" target="_blank">official webs
 ite</a> or follow them on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/thesinkholebeer
 bar/" target="_blank">Facebook</a> and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/t
 hesinkholebeerbar/" target="_blank">Instagram</a>.</p><p></p><p></p><p><str
 ong>About Don’t Call Me Betty:</strong> Formed in 2010\, Don’t Call Me Bett
 y is composed of local professionals\, including Indiana University faculty
  and an optometrist\, who share a passion for rock music. Their diverse set
 list covers hits from the 1970s to the 2000s\, ensuring a lively and nostal
 gic experience. Learn more about the band on their <a href="https://www.fac
 ebook.com/dontcallmebetty/" target="_blank">Facebook page</a>.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250222T184920Z
LOCATION:The Sinkhole Craft Beer Bar\, 313 E Winslow Rd\, Bloomington\, IN 
 47401\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:The Sinkhole Craft Beer Bar 5th Anniversary with Don't Call Me Bett
 y
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
