UID:7tneh68v7nlr4vq0coo2cun90j@google.com
X-GOOGLE-CONFERENCE:https://meet.google.com/jya-hovz-jqe
CREATED:20240322T135804Z
DESCRIPTION:On the eve before the 2024 Solar Eclipse\, join us for a cosmic
  trance dance with live music at Touchstone Wellness Center. This immersive
  event is a guided exploration inward\, designed to unlock a flow state. Mu
 sic and dance serve as tools for healing\, transcendence\, and transformati
 on. <br><br>The event will feature dance facilitation by Utam Moses and liv
 e music by The SomaVibe band &quot\;The Inner Space&quot\; with members Ste
 phanie Heidemann (Wyld Vocals)\, Tom Clark (Flutes)\, Charlie Jesseph (Guit
 ar/Vocals)\, Norbert Herber (Keyboards/Sound design)\, and Julian Douglas (
