UID:e1021308113092905@facebook.com
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/1021308113092905/
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20241228T191337Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we come together to celebrate the incredible life an
 d legacy of Janis Stockhouse. This gathering is an opportunity for all who 
 loved her dearly to share stories\, enjoy music\, and honor her lasting imp
 act on our lives and the world of music.\n\nWe’ve started a Google Drive fo
 r anyone who would like to contribute photos of/with Janis. Let’s build a b
 eautiful collection of memories that showcase the joy and inspiration she b
 rought to our lives. \n\nhttps://drive.google.com/drive/folders/106_hdyChW9
 7PStJ7cAGbSmAFpb8yyhov?usp=drive_link\n\nPlease note\, this will be the onl
 y local service. A private family service will be held in Wisconsin\, where
  her final tribute will take place at her parents' cemetery.\n\nMore detail
 s will be shared as they come together. For now\, we hope you’ll join us to
  celebrate the extraordinary life of a woman who gave so much to all of us.
 \n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/events/1021308113092905/
LAST-MODIFIED:20250117T155548Z
LOCATION:Ray E. Cramer Marching Hundred Hall
SEQUENCE:7742
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Music & Memories: A Tribute to Janis Stockhouse
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
