 sician\, poet\, storyteller\, or just a fan of local talent\, this cozy com
 munity event is the perfect midweek reset. Perform or simply enjoy the show
  — all are welcome.</p><p>Enjoy sweet and savory snacks\, beer\, and non-al
 coholic drinks while you listen in a relaxed café setting. No cover\, no pr
 essure — just good vibes\, great company\, and a rotating lineup of local v
 oices. </p>
