DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>🎶 Honoring a Legacy of Music\, Mentorship\, and Com
 munity</strong></p><p>Join us for a heartfelt tribute concert honoring the 
 legacy of <strong>Janis Stockhouse</strong>\, a beloved band director who i
 nspired generations of musicians.<br>📅 <strong>November 29\, 2025\, at 6:0
 0 PM</strong><br>📍 <strong>Bloomington High School North Auditorium</stron
 g></p><p>Alumni from her band program—spanning generations and traveling fr
 om across the country—will gather to celebrate her impact through music. Th
 e evening will feature performances by <strong>symphonic and jazz band ense
 mbles</strong>.</p><p>Come share in the joy of music and remembrance as we 
 pay tribute to an extraordinary educator and friend.</p><p>More info: <a hr
 ef="https://stockhouseconcert.org">https://stockhouseconcert.org</a></p><p>
 <strong>🎥 Other Janis Stockhouse Tributes</strong></p><p>• <strong>Celebra
 tion of Life Service</strong><br>Ray E. Cramer Marching Hundred Hall\, Bloo
 mington\, IN<br>🎞️ Video by Duane Busick<br>Watch on YouTube: <a href="htt
 ps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KzsRwiJcGNY">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K
 zsRwiJcGNY</a></p><p>• <strong>WFIU: Remembering Janis Stockhouse</strong><
 br>🎙️ <em>Just You and Me</em> program hosted by David Brent Johnson<br>Co
 ntributors: Lissa May\, Rachel Caswell\, Natalie Boeyink\, Sara Caswell\, a
 nd Thomas Wilson<br>Part 1: <a href="https://indianapublicmedia.org/nightli
 ghts/remembering-janis-stockhouse.php">https://indianapublicmedia.org/night
 lights/remembering-janis-stockhouse.php</a><br>Part 2: <a href="https://ind
 ianapublicmedia.org/nightlights/remembering-janis-stockhouse-part-2.php">ht
 tps://indianapublicmedia.org/nightlights/remembering-janis-stockhouse-part-
 2.php</a></p><p>• <strong>Herald-Times Article</strong><br>📰 <em>Janis Sto
 ckhouse\, legendary music director\, mentor\, dies at 69</em><br><a href="h
 ttps://www.heraldtimesonline.com/story/news/local/2024/12/28/janis-stockhou
 se-bloomington-band-director-educator-dies-at-69/77267725007/">https://www.
 heraldtimesonline.com/story/news/local/2024/12/28/janis-stockhouse-blooming
 ton-band-director-educator-dies-at-69/77267725007/</a></p><p>• <strong>Stro
 ng Songs Podcast</strong><br>🎧 2019 interview with Janis Stockhouse by Kir
 k Hamilton<br>Outro solo by BJ Cord<br><a href="https://strongsongspodcast.
 com/episode/remembering-janis-stockhouse-the-great-band-director">https://s
 trongsongspodcast.com/episode/remembering-janis-stockhouse-the-great-band-d
 irector</a></p><p>• <strong>The Real Deal Podcast</strong><br>🎤 Interview 
 with Janis Stockhouse (Fall 2024)<br>Hosted by Rick and Connor Granlund<br>
 <a href="https://lnns.co/OHFxUz5eds3">https://lnns.co/OHFxUz5eds3</a></p>
