DESCRIPTION:Eric Brown and the Boat Drinkers:  Wasted away in Margaritavill
 e Show\, Jimmy Buffet\, and Beach Party Music\n\nFREE ADMISSION\nBRING YOUR
  LAWNCHAIRS AND BLANKETS\nFOOD TRUCKS ON SITE\n\nIn partnership with the To
 wn of Ellettsville\, B97 and Hoosier Country 105.1 is thrilled to launch a 
 new Summer Concert Series from May 24\, 2025 through July 26\, 2025 from 6 
 pm to 8:30 pm at Marci Jane Lewis Park in Ellettsville. Admission is FREE\,
  and food trucks will be on site for food & beverage purchases. Mark your c
 alendar now so you don't miss great live music every Saturday--bring your l
 awn chairs or blanket\, get comfortable\, and enjoy! Sponsors will be on si
 te with swag & giveaways\, and intermission will feature games & prizes!\n\
 nIn case of bad weather\, concerts will move to Seven Oaks Classical School
  Gymnasium\, announced on-air by WBWB & WHCC\, at wbwb.com & whcc105.com\, 
 and on social media.\n\nBrought to you by:\n\nHeadliner: Smithville Communi
 cations\n\nSupporting Act: IU Credit Union\, Master Rental\, Johnny’s Signs
 \n\nSpotlight: Coghlan Orthodontics\, Rapid Roofing and Restoration\, Carpe
 ts Plus Color Tile\, The People’s State Bank\, E Z Leasing and Rentals\, Th
 e Chocolate Moose and No Dishes Podcast\, Seven Oaks Classical School\, and
  Town of Ellettsville\, IN\n\nFront Row: Chandler Funeral Home\, Premier Ca
 binet Design\, Tony Kinser Body Shop\, Overhead Door Company of Bloomington
 \, Alternative Care Solutions\, Style Encore & Once Upon a Child\, Rumpke W
 aste and Recycling\, Spectrum Creative Group\, Nite Owl Promotions\, Phat D
 addy’s BBQ\n\nFan Club: IU Athletics\, Bell’s Vacuum and Appliance\, Til De
 ath Tattoo and Piercing Parlor\, Office Easel Promotions\, Dave and Busters
 \, Insight Optical\, CenterPoint Energy\, Menards\, Hampton Inn\n\nGroupie:
  Mad 4 My Dog\, Neal Tire & Auto Service\, Hoosier Family Eye Care Center\n
 \nhttps://www.facebook.com/events/1021679303277086/
